room_title: Escape room "Escape the Niagara" by Escape Game Erie in Erie
room_description: Lake Erie is under siege, and your group of spies is the only hope! The flagship Niagara has lagged behind. You must inform your fellow comrades of the trap being prepared by the British, but first, you'll have to escape from their grasp yourself! Can you escape or will you go down with the ship?
